# Cubism Live2D SDK (60+ MB). The avatar feature is optional and
# vite.config.ts falls back to src/stubs/cubism/ when the folder is
# absent, so the pilot/staging build ships without it. If you want
# the Live2D avatar in a build, remove this exclusion.
CubismSdkForWeb-5-r.4/
